{"tid":2454914,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"通過催眠術進行通靈及前世回溯的科學基礎","createTime":"2021-03-20T15:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T12:57:43.000Z","uid":389615,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c85d05cd7708c09fb745ab6011ba616812421b4b","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:20:39.000Z","msg":"心理學家發現，人腦可分意識和潛意識部分<br />\n潛意識主宰我們生活<br />\n一般人很難跟自己潛意識溝通<br />\n所以當你想戒零食 但你發覺你好難戒<br />\n因為你意識明白零食不健康，但潛意識不懂<br />\n<br />\n催眠可以同潛意識溝通<br />\n呢樣有些科學根據<br />\n最簡單係，催眠師可以透過催眠，進行麻醉<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/04/080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fchina%2Flifeintheuk%2Fstory%2F2008%2F04%2F080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f01b5c5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/04/080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/33046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F33046&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=57784486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/33046</a><br />\n<br />\n哈佛大學也有講催眠治療的成效<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.health.harvard.edu/newsletter_article/Hypnosis_as_mental_health_therapy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fnewsletter_article%2FHypnosis_as_mental_health_therapy&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=cd0d206e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.health.harvard.edu/newsletter_article/Hypnosis_as_mental_health_therapy</a><br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁我們可唔可以讓潛意識與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n我們知道我們根本沒法與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n但可否透過催眠，與潛意識溝通，然後再讓潛意識與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n<br />\n現在開始很興前世回溯，透過催眠來找自己的前世記憶<br />\n<br />\n我們可否叫潛意識與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n然後再叫自己靈魂與靈界溝通 <br />\n即係通靈呢<br />\n<br />\n示意圖如下: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rtxscJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrtxscJb.jpg&h=82d687f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關前世記憶的研究和新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/591330/%E6%97%A53%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%89%8B%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E5%B0%8B%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA-%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E8%B6%85%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25BD%2590%2F591330%2F%25E6%2597%25A53%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%2586%25B6%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%2596%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA-%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%25A9%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=5f05249f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/591330/%E6%97%A53%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%89%8B%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E5%B0%8B%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA-%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E8%B6%85%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/3219637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Flifestyle%2F3219637&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=ff3285e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/3219637</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://health.tvbs.com.tw/medical/317228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.tvbs.com.tw%2Fmedical%2F317228&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=a87cb8da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health.tvbs.com.tw/medical/317228</a>"},{"pid":"805b3459599eea2f67b2e5aebbe6a3e6f6268bdb","tid":2454914,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa8845bf342f077ccc8c690720cbab0d7eb78b3","tid":2454914,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:29:42.000Z","msg":"弱撚智"},{"pid":"dd0cff2d5cf88328cb48361031da8a38a606d0e4","tid":2454914,"uid":62841,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"其實唔需要夾硬同科學掛鈎😅😅"},{"pid":"20def6e9642d93206a97b39429f6772c0f734742","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"其實只係睇到呢一個人的回憶，唔等於就係前世呢個慨念"},{"pid":"cb001ada38549d40b6b1dbcea1c0fb684af45aba","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"dd0cff2d5cf88328cb48361031da8a38a606d0e4","tid":2454914,"uid":62841,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"其實唔需要夾硬同科學掛鈎😅😅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:57:48.000Z","msg":"點講？潛意識係科學，但靈界和前世暫時唔係科學。<br />\n不過現在好多人會嘗試用各種可與潛意識溝通的方法，來嘗試與靈魂溝通，並做一些記憶回溯，搵有無前世。<br />\n不過其實實驗也證明左，係進行記憶回溯的時候，有機會出現錯誤記憶甚至虛構記憶。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，催眠所得到的信息，可以係真假混合，例如童年回溯80%真再加20%潛意識幻想。對於前世回溯，可能10%真90%假。<br />\n<br />\n由於前世回溯和通靈野難以證實。個人認為可以綜合多方的說法，信「大方向」，即係信人有前世來世和有靈魂機會唔低，但不應信細節（具體輪迴機制就唔好信啦）。"},{"pid":"3dd3c4c718e24fb30187feab7cbe5dfa64117661","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"20def6e9642d93206a97b39429f6772c0f734742","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"其實只係睇到呢一個人的回憶，唔等於就係前世呢個慨念"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"咁點解釋呢樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F3%2Fn9494441.htm&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f9bcfca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm</a>"},{"pid":"900d2a53ba4aafa3aa91cad533658c7bd0a308c3","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3dd3c4c718e24fb30187feab7cbe5dfa64117661","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"20def6e9642d93206a97b39429f6772c0f734742","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"其實只係睇到呢一個人的回憶，唔等於就係前世呢個慨念"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"咁點解釋呢樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F3%2Fn9494441.htm&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f9bcfca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"試咁諗<br />\n如果一個人能夠諗起兩個人既回憶<br />\n仲要呢兩個人都係同一時空<br />\n<br />\n咁唔通呢兩個人都係佢前世？"},{"pid":"a579b0691774248de17d2efb15879e5fee1d730c","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3dd3c4c718e24fb30187feab7cbe5dfa64117661","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"20def6e9642d93206a97b39429f6772c0f734742","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"其實只係睇到呢一個人的回憶，唔等於就係前世呢個慨念"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"咁點解釋呢樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F3%2Fn9494441.htm&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f9bcfca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"人軀體係部收音機<br />\n<br />\n正常只會收到一個channel A<br />\n<br />\n但如果部收音機有d問題，可能會收錯channel B曾經留低的回播<br />\n<br />\n但你唔可以話呢個channel B就係之前既channel A開台前講既野<br />\n<br />\nchannel A B都終有一日會關台<br />\n<br />\n佢地講過既野 只會成為歷史<br />\n<br />\n一d 重要的記憶，會以訊號形式係大氣中不停反彈折射，結果有一日彈番落地面比一部收音機收到"},{"pid":"0bcf049ebd8cd7c3b0ad21818818a4ac034381dd","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a579b0691774248de17d2efb15879e5fee1d730c","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3dd3c4c718e24fb30187feab7cbe5dfa64117661","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"20def6e9642d93206a97b39429f6772c0f734742","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"其實只係睇到呢一個人的回憶，唔等於就係前世呢個慨念"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"咁點解釋呢樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F3%2Fn9494441.htm&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f9bcfca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"人軀體係部收音機<br />\n<br />\n正常只會收到一個channel A<br />\n<br />\n但如果部收音機有d問題，可能會收錯channel B曾經留低的回播<br />\n<br />\n但你唔可以話呢個channel B就係之前既channel A開台前講既野<br />\n<br />\nchannel A B都終有一日會關台<br />\n<br />\n佢地講過既野 只會成為歷史<br />\n<br />\n一d 重要的記憶，會以訊號形式係大氣中不停反彈折射，結果有一日彈番落地面比一部收音機收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T21:48:12.000Z","msg":"你講的呢個，比起有前世或真通靈的可能性更低喎。更違反現時的科學知識，更不可思議，更超自然。"},{"pid":"8e7da164cf2c6ad7674daff835f6d6be04928362","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0bcf049ebd8cd7c3b0ad21818818a4ac034381dd","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a579b0691774248de17d2efb15879e5fee1d730c","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3dd3c4c718e24fb30187feab7cbe5dfa64117661","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"咁點解釋呢樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F3%2Fn9494441.htm&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f9bcfca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"人軀體係部收音機<br />\n<br />\n正常只會收到一個channel A<br />\n<br />\n但如果部收音機有d問題，可能會收錯channel B曾經留低的回播<br />\n<br />\n但你唔可以話呢個channel B就係之前既channel A開台前講既野<br />\n<br />\nchannel A B都終有一日會關台<br />\n<br />\n佢地講過既野 只會成為歷史<br />\n<br />\n一d 重要的記憶，會以訊號形式係大氣中不停反彈折射，結果有一日彈番落地面比一部收音機收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T21:48:12.000Z","msg":"你講的呢個，比起有前世或真通靈的可能性更低喎。更違反現時的科學知識，更不可思議，更超自然。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T21:51:54.000Z","msg":"我意思係比有前世更加 extraordinary"},{"pid":"fa02c46f3ebd7c7df76296eb211e6878a13b6029","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"中國都有所謂的3魂7魄<br />\n<br />\n以下為引述：<br />\n------<br />\n天魂歸天路，到達空間天路。因天魂只是良知亦是不生不滅的「無極」，因有肉體的因果牽連，所以不能歸宗源地，只好被帶走上空間天路的寄託處，暫為其主神收押，這是所謂的「天牢」。<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 地魂歸地府，到達地獄，因地魂可知主魂的一切之因果報應，也可指使在世肉身之善惡，所以肉身死亡後，地魂再進因果是非之地。<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 人魂則徘徊於墓地之間，因人魂本來是「祖德」歷代姓氏流傳接代之肉身。以七魄在身其性行之魄力，死亡後再墓地對神主，來來往往之走上人路之寄託處。<br />\n<br />\n直到再度輪迴，三魂才會重聚。而「三魂」的根本是「真如」（生命實相），「三魂」是由於「真如動念」所產生的一種能量形態並吸附了靈質而具形體，屬於「靈界」。<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/culture/bl429ko.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fculture%2Fbl429ko.html&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=71f520c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/culture/bl429ko.html</a><br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n三魂重聚，如果呢3魂並非完全的前3魂所組成<br />\n<br />\nfor example： <br />\nA，B，C 3個人<br />\n共有<br />\nA天魂，A地魂，A人魂<br />\nB天魂，B地魂，B人魂<br />\nC天魂，C地魂，C人魂<br />\n再組合成人既時侯就係<br />\n<br />\nD=A天魂，B地魂，C人魂<br />\nE=B天魂，C地魂，A人魂<br />\nF=C天魂，A地魂，B人魂<br />\n<br />\n咁你仲會唔會話A係D，E，F既前世"},{"pid":"d90edb6cfe99c0d5920e3b40b021e7567865ed25","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa02c46f3ebd7c7df76296eb211e6878a13b6029","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"中國都有所謂的3魂7魄<br />\n<br />\n以下為引述：<br />\n------<br />\n天魂歸天路，到達空間天路。因天魂只是良知亦是不生不滅的「無極」，因有肉體的因果牽連，所以不能歸宗源地，只好被帶走上空間天路的寄託處，暫為其主神收押，這是所謂的「天牢」。<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 地魂歸地府，到達地獄，因地魂可知主魂的一切之因果報應，也可指使在世肉身之善惡，所以肉身死亡後，地魂再進因果是非之地。<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 人魂則徘徊於墓地之間，因人魂本來是「祖德」歷代姓氏流傳接代之肉身。以七魄在身其性行之魄力，死亡後再墓地對神主，來來往往之走上人路之寄託處。<br />\n<br />\n直到再度輪迴，三魂才會重聚。而「三魂」的根本是「真如」（生命實相），「三魂」是由於「真如動念」所產生的一種能量形態並吸附了靈質而具形體，屬於「靈界」。<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/culture/bl429ko.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fculture%2Fbl429ko.html&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=71f520c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/culture/bl429ko.html</a><br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n三魂重聚，如果呢3魂並非完全的前3魂所組成<br />\n<br />\nfor example： <br />\nA，B，C 3個人<br />\n共有<br />\nA天魂，A地魂，A人魂<br />\nB天魂，B地魂，B人魂<br />\nC天魂，C地魂，C人魂<br />\n再組合成人既時侯就係<br />\n<br />\nD=A天魂，B地魂，C人魂<br />\nE=B天魂，C地魂，A人魂<br />\nF=C天魂，A地魂，B人魂<br />\n<br />\n咁你仲會唔會話A係D，E，F既前世"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"咪話你個例子比正常的前世更更加 extraordinary lor"},{"pid":"cce38ebbad0becb4167476b8d70d3c443aa5f473","tid":2454914,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c85d05cd7708c09fb745ab6011ba616812421b4b","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:20:39.000Z","msg":"心理學家發現，人腦可分意識和潛意識部分<br />\n潛意識主宰我們生活<br />\n一般人很難跟自己潛意識溝通<br />\n所以當你想戒零食 但你發覺你好難戒<br />\n因為你意識明白零食不健康，但潛意識不懂<br />\n<br />\n催眠可以同潛意識溝通<br />\n呢樣有些科學根據<br />\n最簡單係，催眠師可以透過催眠，進行麻醉<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/04/080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fchina%2Flifeintheuk%2Fstory%2F2008%2F04%2F080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f01b5c5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/04/080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/33046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F33046&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=57784486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/33046</a><br />\n<br />\n哈佛大學也有講催眠治療的成效<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.health.harvard.edu/newsletter_article/Hypnosis_as_mental_health_therapy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fnewsletter_article%2FHypnosis_as_mental_health_therapy&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=cd0d206e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.health.harvard.edu/newsletter_article/Hypnosis_as_mental_health_therapy</a><br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁我們可唔可以讓潛意識與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n我們知道我們根本沒法與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n但可否透過催眠，與潛意識溝通，然後再讓潛意識與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n<br />\n現在開始很興前世回溯，透過催眠來找自己的前世記憶<br />\n<br />\n我們可否叫潛意識與自己靈魂溝通<br />\n然後再叫自己靈魂與靈界溝通 <br />\n即係通靈呢<br />\n<br />\n示意圖如下: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rtxscJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrtxscJb.jpg&h=82d687f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關前世記憶的研究和新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/591330/%E6%97%A53%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%89%8B%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E5%B0%8B%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA-%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E8%B6%85%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25BD%2590%2F591330%2F%25E6%2597%25A53%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%2586%25B6%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%2596%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA-%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%25A9%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=5f05249f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/591330/%E6%97%A53%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%96%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%89%8B%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E5%B0%8B%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA-%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E8%B6%85%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/3219637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Flifestyle%2F3219637&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=ff3285e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/3219637</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://health.tvbs.com.tw/medical/317228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.tvbs.com.tw%2Fmedical%2F317228&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=a87cb8da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health.tvbs.com.tw/medical/317228</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"邊位心理學家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講Freud啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冰山理論係佢假設咋<br />\n<br />\n同發現係兩個概念<br />\n而現代科學驗證唔到Freud講既野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Freud講既野更加唔符合現代科學研究既標準<br />\n<br />\n潛意識係有 但現代心理學大部份講既潛意識係從認知心理學觀點出發而唔係Psychoanalyais角度出發<br />\n<br />\nNeuroscience對人腦同潛意識現時只可以解答到Easy Problem 對意識既 Hard Problem基本上可以話一無所知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>心理學家發現，人腦可分意識和潛意識部分<br />\n潛意識主宰我們生活<br />\n一般人很難跟自己潛意識溝通<br />\n所以當你想戒零食 但你發覺你好難戒<br />\n因為你意識明白零食不健康，但潛意識不懂</strong>"},{"pid":"3d1d2a74e4c17fe1d706e465dfcca1c9bae57cf1","tid":2454914,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd0cff2d5cf88328cb48361031da8a38a606d0e4","tid":2454914,"uid":62841,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"其實唔需要夾硬同科學掛鈎😅😅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:35:48.000Z","msg":"咪同容格講果啲潛意識同集體潛意識一樣"},{"pid":"c70840fdd66fe143cb75fff915a1b425efb035e2","tid":2454914,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a579b0691774248de17d2efb15879e5fee1d730c","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3dd3c4c718e24fb30187feab7cbe5dfa64117661","tid":2454914,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"20def6e9642d93206a97b39429f6772c0f734742","tid":2454914,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"其實只係睇到呢一個人的回憶，唔等於就係前世呢個慨念"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"咁點解釋呢樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F3%2Fn9494441.htm&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f9bcfca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/3/n9494441.htm</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"人軀體係部收音機<br />\n<br />\n正常只會收到一個channel A<br />\n<br />\n但如果部收音機有d問題，可能會收錯channel B曾經留低的回播<br />\n<br />\n但你唔可以話呢個channel B就係之前既channel A開台前講既野<br />\n<br />\nchannel A B都終有一日會關台<br />\n<br />\n佢地講過既野 只會成為歷史<br />\n<br />\n一d 重要的記憶，會以訊號形式係大氣中不停反彈折射，結果有一日彈番落地面比一部收音機收到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完FMP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"446fa953c28a26725d6e080168bfa534c26040e9","tid":2454914,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote